&nbsp;
Israel is obliged to destroy Hamas and bring the hostages home, "we are working on these two tasks and are determined to do both things," "it will take all the time necessary, but we have to complete this task." Israeli Defence Minister Yoav Gallant said this by speaking with soldiers on an Israeli military base. "I don't think there's an army in the world that can do what you do for these purposes and quality," he added.
